If `‖x(t)‖ = √(‖IC.x₀‖^2 + ‖IC.v₀‖^2 / ‖S.ω‖^2)`, then `‖x(t)‖^2 = ‖IC.x₀‖^2 + ‖IC.v₀‖^2 / ‖S.ω‖^2`.

Substituting into the identity:
`‖IC.x₀‖^2 + ‖IC.v₀‖^2 / ‖S.ω‖^2 + ‖v(t)‖^2 = ‖IC.x₀‖^2 + ‖IC.v₀‖^2 / ‖S.ω‖^2`
`‖v(t)‖^2 = 0`
`‖v(t)‖ = 0`
`v(t) = 0`

This completes the proof.

