        have ht9 : tan (S.omega * t.val) = sin (S.omega * t.val) / cos (S.omega * t.val) := by
          rw [tan_eq_sin_div_cos]
        rw [ht9]
        all_goals
          ring_nf
    rw [ht4]
```

Now, we need to compute the norm of ` (1 / cos (S.omega * t.val)) • IC.x₀ `

```tactics
