    field_simp [h1, hcos] at *
    nlinarith [htan]
  rw [htan']
  all_goals ring_nf
```

Now, compute the squared norm.
`‖(IC.trajectory S) t‖^2 = ‖IC.x₀‖^2 + ‖IC.v₀‖^2 / S.ω^2`
This is true.

```tactics
